headline: D.R. Horton's Charlotte South Division Announces Grand Opening Celebration in Richburg, SC on February 11
summary: New Home Community Offering Ranch and Two-Story Single-Family Homes RICHBURG, SC / ACCESS Newswire / February 9, 2026 / A new community, perfectly located south of Charlotte and within reach of local conveniences, is preparing to welcome residents. ...
